WEBVTT

01:31.700 --> 01:35.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:35.980 --> 01:38.980
[Episode 15]

01:57.000 --> 01:58.180
Kill everyone

01:59.150 --> 02:00.230
but the children.

02:01.510 --> 02:02.130
Don't go there!

02:06.680 --> 02:07.210
Don't go there...

02:08.340 --> 02:12.140
♪Like fleeting shadows, a hundred years slip by♪

02:12.300 --> 02:18.580
♪Let love and hate drift out of sight♪

02:18.940 --> 02:25.420
♪I walk into a heartbreak burning bright♪

02:25.740 --> 02:32.620
♪Crash into a heart wall, bitter and soft♪

02:32.700 --> 02:35.820
♪Tears slowly turn to frost♪

02:36.180 --> 02:39.780
♪Fading to white, all is lost♪

02:40.060 --> 02:47.340
♪When I wake, who's by my side?♪

02:52.080 --> 02:53.380
Mother!

02:57.840 --> 02:58.890
Mother!

03:01.750 --> 03:02.500
Mother!

03:04.310 --> 03:04.890
Stop!

03:39.030 --> 03:39.690
You wear painted skins?

03:42.280 --> 03:43.660
You're not from the Shilin Sect.

03:48.030 --> 03:48.940
Who are you exactly?

03:50.430 --> 03:51.340
What are you after?

04:40.310 --> 04:41.220
The Frost Spell.

04:41.920 --> 04:42.660
The Formless Moon Sect.

04:51.480 --> 04:52.250
Wu Wangyan?

05:04.750 --> 05:06.170
You always wanted to know

05:06.870 --> 05:08.580
what secret I was hiding.

05:10.430 --> 05:12.140
Now you have your answer.

05:25.950 --> 05:26.900
The Star Stone...

05:29.070 --> 05:30.010
Give it back!

05:31.890 --> 05:32.610
Dream on.

05:56.240 --> 05:56.810
The sachet...

06:04.880 --> 06:05.560
Oh no!

06:47.000 --> 06:48.340
Threatening me with him won't work.

06:49.560 --> 06:50.870
I can't undo the petrification.

06:52.630 --> 06:53.370
I can't do it.

06:54.070 --> 06:55.300
Then I'll kill him!

07:03.920 --> 07:06.220
The stone thorn has my runes on it.

07:06.920 --> 07:08.100
If I cast the spell...

07:10.000 --> 07:11.420
you'll die instantly.

07:12.720 --> 07:13.860
Do you choose death,

07:15.160 --> 07:16.980
or do you help me free my people?

08:00.070 --> 08:00.660
Qing Yi!

08:19.480 --> 08:20.570
The Dragon Deity's Power.

08:28.720 --> 08:29.890
You have it,

08:31.480 --> 08:33.260
so why no dragon birthmark?

08:35.120 --> 08:35.930
The Dragon clan...

08:38.320 --> 08:39.090
Birthmark...

08:41.870 --> 08:43.420
Your birthmark is so interesting.

08:43.870 --> 08:45.380
It looks like a heart made of flowing water.

08:45.960 --> 08:47.300
How did I never see it?

08:52.200 --> 08:53.380
You're not Wu Wangyan.

08:54.550 --> 08:55.380
You're not her!

08:57.790 --> 08:59.780
You're looking for a child with a dragon birthmark.

09:03.150 --> 09:04.690
Then I know who you are.

09:06.390 --> 09:07.260
That's right.

09:08.630 --> 09:09.810
She's Jiu Ying.

09:31.720 --> 09:32.420
Little Nine.

09:33.630 --> 09:34.330
Or maybe...

09:36.630 --> 09:38.330
I should call you by your true name...

09:42.750 --> 09:43.330
Jiu Ying.

09:54.480 --> 09:55.540
Who sent you here?

09:56.270 --> 09:57.500
Why pretend to be a Shilin Sect member?

09:58.320 --> 09:59.330
It... it's Jiu Ying.

09:59.960 --> 10:01.210
You know of me?

10:02.360 --> 10:03.660
The first time I saw

10:03.660 --> 10:04.810
those nine spots on you,

10:06.550 --> 10:07.780
I suspected it was you.

10:09.440 --> 10:10.870
Those nine markings on your head

10:10.870 --> 10:11.780
are quite pretty.

10:12.510 --> 10:13.780
So I'll call you

10:14.030 --> 10:14.540
Little Nine.

10:15.870 --> 10:16.570
Later,

10:17.440 --> 10:18.660
you found out

10:18.670 --> 10:20.570
we weren't the real Man Man and Di Zhu.

10:21.270 --> 10:22.420
If you were dead,

10:24.000 --> 10:25.610
those two demons

10:26.720 --> 10:27.690
who possess

10:27.690 --> 10:29.300
Man Man and Di Zhu

10:30.480 --> 10:32.210
would never get the Star Stone.

10:33.000 --> 10:34.450
The only one who could stay by us

10:34.450 --> 10:35.780
and eavesdrop on our every word

10:36.600 --> 10:37.420
was Little Nine.

10:38.670 --> 10:39.540
But Little Nine

10:39.960 --> 10:41.020
was just

10:41.030 --> 10:42.690
an ordinary, harmless snake.

10:43.030 --> 10:43.780
Relax.

10:44.720 --> 10:45.690
The blood didn't turn dark.

10:46.790 --> 10:47.330
So,

10:47.440 --> 10:48.970
I had to wait for you to slip up,

10:49.440 --> 10:50.730
to reveal your true form.

10:51.120 --> 10:52.730
I failed twice...

11:08.270 --> 11:08.970
but in the end,

11:09.440 --> 11:10.570
I caught you.

11:11.320 --> 11:12.330
Just a bit too late,

11:13.790 --> 11:15.780
since you've grown your third head.

11:17.670 --> 11:18.810
I don't quite understand

11:19.030 --> 11:20.060
what you're saying.

11:21.200 --> 11:22.380
But it sounds like

11:23.080 --> 11:24.500
you know me well,

11:26.240 --> 11:28.140
like an old friend.

11:29.600 --> 11:30.450
Indeed.

11:32.270 --> 11:33.260
Very well.

11:35.630 --> 11:37.020
All your scheming,

11:38.550 --> 11:39.660
just to get a look

11:39.720 --> 11:40.730
at my true form?

11:41.440 --> 11:42.810
Because in the end,

11:42.840 --> 11:44.500
you'll become the Demon King,

11:45.510 --> 11:46.570
destroying the whole world,

11:47.270 --> 11:48.930
yet no one knows your origin.

11:50.120 --> 11:50.810
So,

11:51.390 --> 11:52.610
I wanted to find out

11:53.670 --> 11:55.520
what exactly you are.

11:59.550 --> 12:00.420
In the beginning,

12:02.120 --> 12:04.060
I was just a snake egg

12:04.320 --> 12:05.270
buried in this earth

12:05.270 --> 12:06.850
for millions of years, unable to hatch.

12:07.960 --> 12:09.540
The egg was filled with deadly venom.

12:10.120 --> 12:12.000
The Aodeng people migrated here

12:12.120 --> 12:13.730
and were poisoned one after another.

12:14.320 --> 12:16.020
They thought it was a plague.

12:18.150 --> 12:20.570
Then the Star Stone fell from the sky,

12:21.550 --> 12:22.610
bringing heavenly fire.

12:27.670 --> 12:28.780
The heat of the flames

12:29.480 --> 12:30.660
hatched you.

12:31.790 --> 12:32.970
I broke out of my shell,

12:33.440 --> 12:35.060
absorbed the Star Stone's power,

12:35.670 --> 12:36.690
and became a demon.

12:37.480 --> 12:38.780
The egg disappeared.

12:39.240 --> 12:40.810
The Aodeng people stopped getting poisoned.

12:41.670 --> 12:42.850
They thought

12:43.870 --> 12:45.690
it was a blessing from the Star Stone.

12:46.960 --> 12:48.140
After I hatched,

12:49.030 --> 12:50.380
the first person I saw

12:52.080 --> 12:53.090
was Di Zhu.

13:04.390 --> 13:06.140
But I was newly born,

13:06.270 --> 13:07.330
my power weak.

13:07.750 --> 13:09.380
I could only take Di Zhu's blood

13:09.720 --> 13:11.060
and briefly possess her.

13:12.600 --> 13:13.330
That way,

13:13.630 --> 13:16.060
I could go into the cave every night

13:16.910 --> 13:18.330
to absorb the Star Stone's power

13:18.960 --> 13:20.020
and grow stronger.

13:21.550 --> 13:23.730
To keep others from getting the Stone,

13:25.200 --> 13:26.380
you started killing.

13:28.000 --> 13:29.300
The Star Stone's power

13:30.030 --> 13:32.210
gave me a second venomous head.

13:33.720 --> 13:35.380
I smeared venom on a hairpin

13:36.080 --> 13:37.900
to kill those who coveted the Stone.

13:38.750 --> 13:40.420
But the venom couldn't kill demons.

13:41.320 --> 13:42.060
So...

13:44.240 --> 13:45.610
I could only frame you.

13:46.440 --> 13:47.140
Too bad,

13:48.630 --> 13:49.660
you didn't succeed.

13:52.360 --> 13:52.970
True.

13:55.480 --> 13:57.610
But I got something unexpected.

13:59.080 --> 14:00.930
I found a power source

14:01.510 --> 14:03.380
even stronger than the Star Stone.

14:04.600 --> 14:05.450
Killing.

14:06.360 --> 14:07.300
No, not killing.

14:08.240 --> 14:09.180
It's fear.

14:10.270 --> 14:11.660
I realized,

14:12.200 --> 14:13.420
the more people died,

14:13.840 --> 14:15.690
the more the Aodeng people feared,

14:16.790 --> 14:18.090
the stronger I became.

14:21.240 --> 14:22.570
In just a few days,

14:25.630 --> 14:27.420
I've already grown my third head.

14:30.360 --> 14:32.020
Even without the Star Stone,

14:33.240 --> 14:35.330
as long as the world is filled with despair,

14:36.670 --> 14:37.500
fear,

14:38.750 --> 14:39.780
and hatred,

14:40.390 --> 14:42.930
I'll have an endless supply of power.

14:43.670 --> 14:44.610
Soon enough,

14:45.790 --> 14:47.180
all nine of my heads

14:48.440 --> 14:49.810
will be fully grown.

14:55.120 --> 14:57.140
With all nine heads,

14:57.720 --> 14:59.320
Jiu Ying can break each head

14:59.320 --> 15:00.690
into nine spirit fragments.

15:01.480 --> 15:03.970
Eighty-one pieces scattered across the world.

15:04.630 --> 15:05.900
That's why this land

15:06.200 --> 15:07.660
is overrun with people

15:08.120 --> 15:09.610
controlled by Jiu Ying.

15:10.320 --> 15:11.660
The Six-Eyed Butterflies under Jiu Ying

15:12.150 --> 15:13.540
planted pupae inside us.

15:14.080 --> 15:15.260
We have no choice but to obey.

15:16.030 --> 15:17.450
Wu Zhiqi was already going to give the Star Stone

15:17.450 --> 15:18.160
to Jiu Ying,

15:18.390 --> 15:20.180
to bring it to the battlefield and destroy humanity.

15:21.120 --> 15:22.210
Why control you

15:23.750 --> 15:25.090
and arrange for us to steal it?

15:27.120 --> 15:27.690
Because...

15:28.910 --> 15:30.660
the Star Stone wasn't meant to destroy humanity.

15:31.480 --> 15:33.090
It was to make humans and demons

15:33.320 --> 15:34.180
destroy each other.

15:34.720 --> 15:35.450
What?

15:37.120 --> 15:38.900
The Yuan Clay Incident,

15:38.910 --> 15:39.690
which sparked the war,

15:40.080 --> 15:40.900
seemed like an accident,

15:41.200 --> 15:42.570
but it was also schemed by Jiu Ying.

15:46.750 --> 15:48.330
You mean Yuan's death

15:50.390 --> 15:51.420
wasn't an accident?

15:52.270 --> 15:53.210
It wasn't just him.

15:54.000 --> 15:55.020
There are countless others

15:55.020 --> 15:56.180
you'd never suspect

15:56.600 --> 15:57.900
possessed by Jiu Ying's spirit.

15:58.390 --> 15:59.500
They walk among us,

16:00.510 --> 16:02.900
constantly stirring conflict between our races,

16:03.200 --> 16:04.450
igniting battles.

16:04.630 --> 16:06.300
And all this strife and hatred

16:07.840 --> 16:09.610
makes Jiu Ying stronger.

16:10.480 --> 16:11.900
She even slaughtered the nine Dragons.

16:14.910 --> 16:16.850
No wonder they say Jiu Ying can't be killed.

16:17.600 --> 16:18.450
Turns out,

16:19.080 --> 16:20.610
even sealed by the nine dragon sons,

16:21.440 --> 16:22.780
you're still causing chaos.

16:24.000 --> 16:25.380
They thought sealing

16:25.390 --> 16:26.780
my nine heads

16:27.320 --> 16:29.260
would destroy me for good.

16:29.870 --> 16:30.730
Too bad

16:31.840 --> 16:33.020
I'd already scattered

16:33.020 --> 16:34.900
countless spirit fragments across the world.

16:35.870 --> 16:37.140
Each piece

16:38.390 --> 16:40.610
can attach to a living being.

16:49.440 --> 16:50.540
Once it attaches,

16:51.150 --> 16:52.260
it waits for a moment

16:52.260 --> 16:53.320
when the host's mind wavers,

16:53.320 --> 16:54.180
then takes control.

16:54.870 --> 16:56.780
As long as one piece remains,

16:57.320 --> 16:58.810
Jiu Ying cannot die.

16:59.150 --> 17:00.380
You might as well give up.

17:01.910 --> 17:02.380
No.

17:02.870 --> 17:03.610
You're wrong.

17:04.750 --> 17:05.650
The Dragon Deity

17:05.720 --> 17:07.410
will defeat Jiu Ying in the end.

17:08.160 --> 17:09.850
All eighty-one spirit fragments

17:10.240 --> 17:11.740
will be destroyed one by one.

17:12.510 --> 17:14.090
That annoying Shilin Sect

17:14.790 --> 17:16.090
has been hunting

17:16.090 --> 17:18.090
for my spirit fragments.

17:18.720 --> 17:20.460
I have to kill Chi Wen,

17:21.160 --> 17:22.500
break the seal,

17:24.070 --> 17:25.610
and get my heads back.

17:26.830 --> 17:28.690
So you've been searching

17:28.690 --> 17:29.700
for the dragon's descendants.

17:31.070 --> 17:32.810
Because only a dragon...

17:33.790 --> 17:34.610
Can kill a dragon.

17:40.880 --> 17:42.500
The Six-Eyed Butterflies gave us the glowing worm.

17:43.720 --> 17:46.090
Once it's inside the Star Stone,

17:46.400 --> 17:47.510
it will devour

17:47.510 --> 17:49.130
his insides,

17:49.480 --> 17:50.940
make him lose control,

17:51.400 --> 17:52.700
and cause an explosion.

18:09.000 --> 18:09.850
Where's the Star Stone?

18:34.680 --> 18:35.810
What do we do now?

18:36.480 --> 18:37.300
Where are we taking him?

18:38.030 --> 18:38.850
We can't go anywhere.

18:55.880 --> 18:56.700
The Six-Eyed Butterfly...

18:58.680 --> 18:59.700
is actually two people.

19:00.240 --> 19:00.980
That's right.

19:01.240 --> 19:02.300
Unlike you,

19:02.680 --> 19:04.410
we're inseparable,

19:04.790 --> 19:06.780
loving brothers.

19:17.270 --> 19:17.780
Watch out!

19:27.000 --> 19:27.740
You've got it wrong.

19:28.550 --> 19:29.740
We're not with him.

19:30.310 --> 19:31.410
Threatening us with him

19:31.960 --> 19:32.540
won't work.

19:33.000 --> 19:34.130
You should just kill him.

19:35.830 --> 19:36.650
Are you sure?

19:37.640 --> 19:39.300
The look on the person behind you

19:39.590 --> 19:40.980
says otherwise.

19:42.310 --> 19:43.610
If you don't want him dead,

19:43.830 --> 19:44.780
come with us.

19:56.240 --> 19:56.810
Don't forget

19:58.070 --> 19:59.780
he imprisoned you for all those years.

20:02.480 --> 20:03.570
You said earlier

20:04.480 --> 20:06.260
he secretly helped us

20:07.310 --> 20:08.410
by letting me go.

20:13.070 --> 20:14.130
All these years,

20:15.510 --> 20:16.700
in that tiny space,

20:17.400 --> 20:19.130
he was my only friend.

20:29.160 --> 20:30.890
If you no longer care about the Star Stone,

20:31.750 --> 20:33.130
then why did you attack me

20:33.160 --> 20:33.890
at the wedding?

20:43.640 --> 20:47.540
- Kiss! - Kiss!

20:54.110 --> 20:55.060
Come out, Little Nine!

20:56.030 --> 20:57.410
I simply wanted you dead.

21:13.400 --> 21:14.020
Tian Di!

21:29.440 --> 21:30.410
Let Wu Zhiqi go!

21:30.640 --> 21:31.260
Stop!

21:57.830 --> 21:59.460
You're covered in wounds,

22:00.200 --> 22:01.850
yet you can't bear to hurt her.

22:02.640 --> 22:03.740
How devoted.

22:04.750 --> 22:05.940
Let's see

22:07.270 --> 22:08.780
how long you can last.

22:16.660 --> 22:18.500
♪One winter day♪

22:19.180 --> 22:24.140
♪By the lake, a boy in white opened his eyes♪

22:24.860 --> 22:32.340
♪He gazed at the sky, watching fate spin by♪

22:32.420 --> 22:39.820
♪The wind asked why he smiled in silence♪

22:40.220 --> 22:46.580
♪He bowed low, gently offering wildflowers from his heart♪

23:12.160 --> 23:12.740
Don't be rash!

23:21.640 --> 23:22.090
Oh no.

23:22.480 --> 23:23.540
He's losing control of his power!

23:34.830 --> 23:35.330
Tian Di...

23:35.790 --> 23:36.330
No!

23:40.400 --> 23:41.020
Yuan Xizai!

24:13.070 --> 24:15.170
So this is the Star Stone exit Master Bai Ze mentioned?

24:15.680 --> 24:16.540
This stone tablet?

24:17.590 --> 24:18.810
It's Wu Shiguang's master's grave.

24:19.160 --> 24:19.850
Stop bickering.

24:20.440 --> 24:21.170
Quick, smear the blood.

24:21.400 --> 24:22.260
Okay. Got it.

24:22.920 --> 24:24.060
Wu Shiguang would be surprised

24:24.510 --> 24:25.780
that the keepsake of our friendship I kept

24:26.000 --> 24:27.300
would save his life years later.

24:56.310 --> 24:57.460
Why isn't it working?

24:58.510 --> 24:59.780
That liar Bai Ze!

25:03.070 --> 25:03.880
Are they really going to die

25:03.880 --> 25:04.940
in the disasters?

25:36.310 --> 25:36.890
Master...

25:37.640 --> 25:38.740
What's happening?

25:39.200 --> 25:40.170
Father!

25:41.830 --> 25:42.780
Mother!

25:43.030 --> 25:43.540
Shiguang!

26:01.680 --> 26:03.650
Quick, take him and go!

26:04.000 --> 26:04.740
I won't!

26:05.030 --> 26:06.370
I have to save my parents!

26:06.830 --> 26:07.260
Father!

26:24.640 --> 26:25.410
What are you waiting for?

26:25.550 --> 26:26.090
Go after them!

28:16.270 --> 28:16.810
Lu Wuyi!

28:19.860 --> 28:22.140
♪Through a thousand shadows♪

28:23.550 --> 28:24.090
Lu Wuyi!

28:40.200 --> 28:40.650
Oh no.

28:40.680 --> 28:41.740
What's happening to Wu Zhiqi?

28:42.790 --> 28:43.650
The third head,

28:44.270 --> 28:45.400
the head of frenzy.

28:45.690 --> 28:47.280
It drives a person mad,

28:47.790 --> 28:48.740
making their demon power run wild.

28:52.960 --> 28:54.090
If Wu Zhiqi loses control,

28:54.720 --> 28:56.160
it'll cause the Hurricane Catastrophe.

28:58.510 --> 28:59.300
I've figured out

28:59.310 --> 29:00.060
Jiu Ying's origin.

29:00.250 --> 29:00.850
Let's go.

29:01.000 --> 29:02.090
We'll use the Star Stone to leave.

29:03.440 --> 29:04.130
- Okay. - Let's go.

29:06.000 --> 29:06.700
Where's the Star Stone?

29:23.200 --> 29:23.850
You go first.

29:24.590 --> 29:26.090
You can turn into sand and leave.

29:28.400 --> 29:28.980
Let's go together!

30:16.720 --> 30:18.130
Once we get the Star Stone,

30:18.750 --> 30:19.890
we can use our power

30:20.350 --> 30:21.700
to leave the illusion.

30:48.680 --> 30:49.220
You...

30:56.110 --> 30:56.650
He...

30:58.830 --> 30:59.980
He's Yuan Wuhuo,

31:01.440 --> 31:02.370
the butterfly demon.

31:04.160 --> 31:04.940
He went in too?

31:06.200 --> 31:07.500
When the Star Stone's pull

31:07.500 --> 31:08.810
was strongest earlier,

31:09.510 --> 31:11.060
I almost got sucked in.

31:19.720 --> 31:21.060
The butterfly demon hiding in the shadows

31:21.060 --> 31:21.940
pushed me away.

31:22.960 --> 31:24.850
But he got pulled in himself.

31:26.440 --> 31:27.170
So,

31:27.830 --> 31:29.500
in the past they're living in,

31:31.680 --> 31:32.330
who is the true owner

31:32.350 --> 31:33.650
of that time?

31:34.310 --> 31:35.260
That past

31:36.160 --> 31:37.300
was shared

31:37.300 --> 31:38.810
by the two brothers.

31:39.270 --> 31:40.260
They are both the owners,

31:41.070 --> 31:42.330
and witnesses to each other.

31:44.920 --> 31:46.370
You're not Yuan Wuhuo.
[*Wuhuo as in "free of misfortune"]

31:47.680 --> 31:49.460
You're the butterfly demon, Yuan Wuhuo.
[*Wuhuo as in "gaining nothing"]

31:51.160 --> 31:51.650
That's right.

31:53.920 --> 31:55.500
So you've been acting this whole time.

31:57.750 --> 31:58.410
That's right.

31:59.440 --> 32:01.220
How else could I make you lower your guard,

32:01.830 --> 32:03.370
help me get the Star Stone,

32:04.350 --> 32:05.330
and leave this place?

32:07.160 --> 32:09.130
So you were behind it before too.

32:11.200 --> 32:11.780
Exactly.

32:13.640 --> 32:15.330
I tried to kill Tian Di

32:16.920 --> 32:18.740
to turn him back into the Star Stone.

32:19.550 --> 32:20.570
But it didn't work.

32:21.720 --> 32:23.130
All that struggling

32:24.070 --> 32:25.540
was pointless.

32:47.720 --> 32:49.260
Did you really think

32:51.160 --> 32:52.370
I was your brother?

32:54.440 --> 32:55.220
Aren't you?

32:56.680 --> 32:57.330
No.

33:00.160 --> 33:02.170
Then why do you look exactly like me?

33:03.590 --> 33:04.540
You're wrong.

33:07.590 --> 33:09.060
Know your place.

33:10.590 --> 33:12.780
You look like me.

33:14.550 --> 33:15.130
I...

33:15.820 --> 33:19.140
♪Who paints the moon in light of day?♪

33:19.660 --> 33:23.660
♪In silver glow, I'm black and white...♪

33:23.680 --> 33:25.330
Who am I?

33:28.000 --> 33:29.780
You'll never know.

33:29.940 --> 33:34.100
♪Tell me why these hands won't let go...♪

33:34.110 --> 33:35.890
Stay here forever.

33:37.100 --> 33:38.540
♪Black and white, they say♪

33:38.980 --> 33:41.700
♪Love and hate just twist and fade♪

33:42.140 --> 33:43.580
♪All these words we write♪

33:43.940 --> 33:47.140
♪Still can't show my shade♪

33:47.380 --> 33:49.620
♪Whose regret♪

33:49.900 --> 33:52.100
♪Calls out my name?♪

33:52.460 --> 33:57.020
♪Chasing shadows, I slip away♪

33:58.300 --> 34:01.540
♪Who would turn their vows to bitter wine?♪

34:02.140 --> 34:06.300
♪An aging hero holds the falling light♪

34:07.780 --> 34:12.260
♪One last beat, one spark, one burning fire♪

34:12.420 --> 34:17.020
♪See the night ignite in flame♪

34:17.100 --> 34:18.700
♪Black and white, they say♪

34:19.020 --> 34:21.820
♪Rivers run and drift away...♪

34:22.440 --> 34:23.540
Yuan Xizai!

34:23.980 --> 34:27.140
♪Then just fade away♪

34:27.380 --> 34:29.620
♪If I cross that line♪

34:29.900 --> 34:32.140
♪Past the hills of time...♪

34:32.440 --> 34:33.500
Why did I lose my power?

34:33.880 --> 34:34.940
Quick, heal him!

34:35.440 --> 34:35.940
Hurry!

34:36.800 --> 34:37.250
Xizai!

34:37.550 --> 34:38.020
Xizai!

34:39.360 --> 34:39.940
Save him!

34:40.670 --> 34:41.420
Save him!

34:42.460 --> 34:47.940
♪I just need you to remember me♪

34:56.710 --> 34:57.570
I can't hold it together much longer.

34:58.550 --> 34:59.940
The Star Stone must not shatter.

35:00.840 --> 35:02.380
I still need it to save my people.

35:03.000 --> 35:04.020
Is there any way?

35:05.150 --> 35:05.570
Yes.

35:06.400 --> 35:06.980
What is it?

35:09.510 --> 35:10.170
What is it?

35:11.110 --> 35:11.940
The Dragon Deity's Power.

35:13.280 --> 35:14.420
It can restore anything,

35:15.070 --> 35:16.170
and bring the dead back to life.

35:26.400 --> 35:27.460
Dragon hearts as one,

35:28.800 --> 35:29.860
all to source return,

35:31.760 --> 35:32.860
all barriers break!

36:06.760 --> 36:07.900
Dragon hearts as one,

36:09.150 --> 36:10.170
all to source return,

36:11.280 --> 36:12.380
all barriers break!

36:44.550 --> 36:45.690
Master Jiu Ying truly has

36:46.070 --> 36:47.500
flawless foresight.

36:52.190 --> 36:54.090
I infused my demonic energy

36:54.230 --> 36:55.730
into a fragment of the Star Stone.

36:56.710 --> 36:59.540
Once it joins with the piece Wu Zhiqi has,

37:00.190 --> 37:01.530
the entire Star Stone

37:01.920 --> 37:03.540
will shatter completely.

37:05.360 --> 37:07.770
Wu Zhiqi will surely sacrifice himself,

37:08.280 --> 37:10.650
releasing the Dragon Deity's Power to fix it.

37:11.360 --> 37:13.900
Then you'll have your chance to seize his power.

37:53.630 --> 37:54.820
Give up.

37:55.630 --> 37:57.210
Take after Xiaowei,

37:58.550 --> 38:00.060
and you'll share her fate.

38:16.070 --> 38:16.860
Bai Ze,

38:17.360 --> 38:19.420
you already gave seventy percent of your power

38:19.800 --> 38:21.650
to that false Dragon Deity.

38:22.320 --> 38:23.860
And you used another twenty percent

38:24.150 --> 38:25.770
to fix the Star Stone.

38:26.760 --> 38:28.420
With the ten percent left,

38:29.190 --> 38:30.770
you want to break my barrier?

38:31.480 --> 38:33.090
What a joke.

38:37.150 --> 38:38.020
Or maybe...

38:41.070 --> 38:42.020
you could try

38:42.030 --> 38:43.690
using the Dragon Deity's Power.

39:03.440 --> 39:04.730
Now we're really trapped here.

39:05.630 --> 39:06.500
It's all my fault.

39:07.800 --> 39:08.570
It's all my fault.

39:09.550 --> 39:10.210
I'm sorry.

39:12.880 --> 39:14.570
At least we know Jiu Ying's origin,

39:15.400 --> 39:16.340
that's something.

39:17.190 --> 39:18.420
And we found out something else,

39:20.360 --> 39:21.130
even better.

39:21.840 --> 39:22.460
What's it?

39:23.670 --> 39:24.420
Jiu Ying's weakness.

39:26.880 --> 39:27.940
What's his weakness?

39:29.440 --> 39:30.860
The same weakness as mine.

39:34.510 --> 39:35.020
Look out!

39:38.230 --> 39:38.820
Ji Ling!

39:39.710 --> 39:40.250
Ji Ling!

39:43.190 --> 39:43.690
Ji Ling!

39:44.230 --> 39:45.060
Hold on to me!

39:45.710 --> 39:46.610
Don't let go!

39:50.480 --> 39:51.090
Lu Wuyi!

39:56.960 --> 39:57.690
What are you doing?

40:01.960 --> 40:02.900
A spike will help...

40:07.420 --> 40:09.340
♪Through a thousand old dreams♪

40:11.820 --> 40:13.740
♪Through a thousand shadows...♪

40:15.320 --> 40:16.980
When disaster strikes,

40:17.550 --> 40:20.020
lovers stay together.

40:23.070 --> 40:24.090
"Live together, die together"?

40:24.590 --> 40:26.290
That's just a story to fool girls.

40:27.030 --> 40:28.250
I don't like him

40:29.000 --> 40:30.020
enough

40:30.020 --> 40:31.100
to die for him.

40:31.100 --> 40:38.900
♪I'll always stay with you♪

40:39.780 --> 40:42.180
♪Don't be sad...♪

40:42.760 --> 40:43.500
The Star Stone!

40:44.180 --> 40:46.580
♪Don't you cry♪

40:46.620 --> 40:48.460
♪Through the darkest nights...♪

40:48.550 --> 40:49.170
Let go!

40:50.360 --> 40:50.940
No!

40:51.800 --> 40:53.130
Let go of the other hand!

40:53.920 --> 40:54.980
Take out the spike!

40:55.670 --> 40:56.500
Trust me!

40:57.300 --> 40:59.660
♪Don't be sad♪

40:59.700 --> 41:01.500
♪Through a thousand broken lights...♪

41:03.230 --> 41:03.900
Let's take a gamble.

41:05.400 --> 41:06.940
If we lose, we just stay here.

41:08.630 --> 41:09.730
And I'll marry you!

41:12.180 --> 41:14.020
♪Stay with you♪

41:15.580 --> 41:19.580
♪See the daylight wrapped in silver light♪

41:20.620 --> 41:23.460
♪Black turns white with time passing by♪

41:24.060 --> 41:28.780
♪She holds a flower, counts the seasons slow♪

41:29.260 --> 41:31.740
♪Waiting for stone to bloom♪

41:32.180 --> 41:36.060
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

41:36.620 --> 41:40.540
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

41:40.940 --> 41:43.900
♪Why's the line we cry to say♪

41:44.780 --> 41:49.180
♪Always "don't you cry"?♪

41:49.700 --> 41:53.460
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

41:54.140 --> 41:57.820
♪Your sunrise fades into my gray♪

41:58.380 --> 42:01.700
♪You left behind your final words♪

42:02.100 --> 42:06.620
♪And every word became a scar♪

42:07.060 --> 42:10.860
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

42:11.500 --> 42:15.500
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

42:15.820 --> 42:18.860
♪Why's the line we cry to say♪

42:19.700 --> 42:24.100
♪Always "don't you cry"?♪

42:24.460 --> 42:28.420
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

42:28.940 --> 42:32.780
♪Your name's the words I long to say♪

42:33.300 --> 42:36.860
♪I call for you, my only one♪

42:37.340 --> 42:44.660
♪You're my everlasting bloom♪

42:45.510 --> 42:46.210
You're here.

43:25.740 --> 43:26.900
♪It's your light♪

43:27.100 --> 43:28.980
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

43:29.140 --> 43:32.260
♪That set the night alight♪

43:32.620 --> 43:39.140
♪And lead me through the fight♪

43:40.900 --> 43:42.780
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

43:43.220 --> 43:47.660
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

43:48.460 --> 43:50.140
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

43:50.300 --> 43:55.700
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

43:56.460 --> 44:01.860
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

44:04.180 --> 44:10.220
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

44:11.180 --> 44:13.340
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

44:13.620 --> 44:18.460
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

44:18.820 --> 44:21.140
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

44:21.340 --> 44:26.420
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

44:26.660 --> 44:28.660
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

44:28.940 --> 44:33.300
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

44:34.300 --> 44:41.260
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

44:57.820 --> 45:00.780
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

45:01.860 --> 45:05.260
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

45:06.060 --> 45:08.580
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

45:08.820 --> 45:11.900
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

45:12.300 --> 45:14.620
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

45:15.140 --> 45:19.540
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

45:19.780 --> 45:21.940
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

45:22.340 --> 45:27.300
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

45:27.540 --> 45:28.700
♪It's your light♪

45:28.900 --> 45:30.740
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

45:30.940 --> 45:34.060
♪That set the night alight♪

45:34.820 --> 45:44.260
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
